# LangChain Course Environment Variables

# Required: OpenAI API Key
# Get your key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here

# Optional: LangSmith (for monitoring and debugging)
# Sign up at: https://smith.langchain.com
# LANGCHAIN_TRACING_V2=true
# LANGCHAIN_API_KEY=your-langsmith-api-key-here
# LANGCHAIN_PROJECT=langchain-course

# Optional: Other LLM Providers
# Uncomment and add keys for providers you want to use

# Anthropic (Claude)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-api-key-here

# Google (Gemini)
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=your-google-api-key-here

# Cohere
# COHERE_API_KEY=your-cohere-api-key-here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace "your-openai-api-key-here" with your actual API key
# 3. Add any other provider keys you want to use
# 4. Never commit your .env file to version control!
